{
  "stem": "26576.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Ah, so we were in that cattle in the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On the way to Sverdlovsk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the way to Sverdlovsk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember sort-- also look, I don't remember it with-- with-- with love.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember that we would at a station run for some food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes we had to change that train for another train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember we would wait for days for another train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember we would put out a coat or a blanket or whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we would sleep there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember I wasn't well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Somehow, my mom told it's rheumatism.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she said she's never seen a young child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But apparently, when I was thinking back later on, I thought it's not rheumatism.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I probably had temperature.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I very often had sore throats.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because later on I also had a lot of problems with my, with my throat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The journey wasn't-- so for me, was a very unpleasant one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But finally we came to that spot after we've changed trains and that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We came to the spot that my father intended, which was called Merke.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This was in Kazakhstan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This is the middle of Asia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was-- look it was also, I used to call it the loft.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You can't imagine what kind of accommodation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, like the huts were made of clay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The floors were clay.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was completely everything there was dust and clay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I've seen later on films like it was very close to the Chinese border, almost on the Chinese border.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the only thing, that my father got a job the way he was thinking.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Because there was a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "This was a big factory, beet root, where they're making sugar out of beet root.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
